'''Cultural Minister''' was a position in the government of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]; this senior bureaucrat was the head of the Imperial Ministry of Culture. The minister as of [[3 ABY/Legends|3.5 ABY]] had ties to [[Xizor/Legends|Xizor]].

